LAYER 1: QUANTUM PARTICLE ENCODING
the substrate made physical
every particle every atom every molecule encoded as qu-septit property vectors
this is where the sea becomes matter

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe 1_quantum.rana


THE FUNDAMENTAL FERMIONS — QUARKS
quarks are never free
they exist only inside composite hadrons
confined by the strong force at 10⁻¹⁵ meters
color charge comes in red green blue
only colorless combinations are stable

